{{! kult-gm-screen/templates/gm-screen.hbs }}
<div class="kult-app-inner">

  {{! Header }}
  <div class="kult-header">
    <div class="kult-title-row">
      <div>
        <div class="kult-title">◈ Kult: Divinity Lost</div>
        <div class="kult-subtitle">Gamemaster's Screen Reference</div>
      </div>
      <button class="kult-cmd-btn" data-tab="chat">⌘ GM Command</button>
    </div>
    <div class="kult-search-row">
      <input id="kult-search" type="text" placeholder="Search moves, rules, tables..." />
    </div>
    <div class="kult-tabs">
      {{#each (array "moves" "rules" "harm" "unique" "npc" "horror" "xp" "chat") as |tab|}}
      <button class="kult-tab {{#if (eq ../currentTab tab)}}active{{/if}}" data-tab="{{tab}}">
        {{#if (eq tab "moves")}}GM Moves{{/if}}
        {{#if (eq tab "rules")}}Rules{{/if}}
        {{#if (eq tab "harm")}}Harm{{/if}}
        {{#if (eq tab "unique")}}Unique Moves{{/if}}
        {{#if (eq tab "npc")}}NPC Builder{{/if}}
        {{#if (eq tab "horror")}}Horror Contract{{/if}}
        {{#if (eq tab "xp")}}Experience{{/if}}
        {{#if (eq tab "chat")}}GM Chat{{/if}}
      </button>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </div>

  {{! Body }}
  <div class="kult-body">

    {{! === MOVES TAB === }}
    <div class="tab-panel {{#if (eq currentTab 'moves')}}active{{/if}}" id="panel-moves">
      {{#each moves as |moveList category|}}
      <div class="kult-section-title">{{capitalize category}} Moves</div>
      <div class="moves-grid">
        {{#each moveList as |move|}}
        <div class="move-chip" data-move="{{move}}" data-type="{{category}}">
          <span class="dot dot-{{category}}"></span>
          <span>{{move}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    {{! === RULES TAB === }}
    <div class="tab-panel {{#if (eq currentTab 'rules')}}active{{/if}}" id="panel-rules">

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">• Keep it Together — roll +Willpower</div>
        <div class="roll-result"><span class="roll-badge rb-15">15+</span><span>You grit your teeth and stay the course.</span></div>
        <div class="roll-result"><span class="roll-badge rb-10">10–14</span><span>Instills a condition (−1 in hindering situations). Choose: angry / sad / scared / guilt-ridden (−1 Stability); obsessed (+1 Relation); distracted (−2); haunted later.</span></div>
        <div class="roll-result"><span class="roll-badge rb-fail">–9</span><span>GM chooses: cower powerless, panic, emotional trauma (−2 Stability), or life-changing trauma (−4 Stability).</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">• Avoid Harm — roll +Reflexes</div>
        <div class="roll-result"><span class="roll-badge rb-15">15+</span><span>Emerge completely unharmed.</span></div>
        <div class="roll-result"><span class="roll-badge rb-10">10–14</span><span>Avoid the worst, but GM decides: bad spot, lose something, or partially sustain Harm.</span></div>
        <div class="roll-result"><span class="roll-badge rb-fail">–9</span><span>Too slow or bad judgment. May not avoid any Harm, or end up in a worse spot. GM makes a Move.</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">• Endure Injury — roll +Fortitude −Harm (add armor rating)</div>
        <div class="roll-result"><span class="roll-badge rb-15">15+</span><span>Ride out the pain and keep going.</span></div>
        <div class="roll-result"><span class="roll-badge rb-10">10–14</span><span>Still standing. GM picks: thrown off balance / lose something / Serious Wound.</span></div>
        <div class="roll-result"><span class="roll-badge rb-fail">–9</span><span>Overwhelming. Choose: knocked out (GM may add Serious Wound) / Critical Wound but act / Die.</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">Stability Track</div>
        <table class="kult-table">
          <thead><tr><th>State</th><th>Effect</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {{#each stability as |row|}}
            <tr class="stab-{{row.tier}}">
              <td>{{row.state}}</td>
              <td>{{row.effect}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">Relation Moves</div>
        <p><strong>Wish No Harm:</strong> Harming a Relation requires Keep it Together. On 10–14: −Relation modifier to damage. On –9: cannot bring yourself to harm them.</p>
        <p><strong>Regain Stability:</strong> Closeness/affirmation from Relation restores Stability steps equal to Relation strength.</p>
        <p><strong>Lose Stability:</strong> Relation seriously injured → lose Stability steps equal to Relation strength. Double if they die.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{! === HARM TAB === }}
    <div class="tab-panel {{#if (eq currentTab 'harm')}}active{{/if}}" id="panel-harm">

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">Wound Penalties (ongoing)</div>
        <table class="kult-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Condition</th><th>Deduction</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {{#each harmData.wounds as |row|}}
            <tr><td>{{row.condition}}</td><td class="harm-val">{{row.deduction}}</td></tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">Typical Harm</div>
        <table class="kult-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Circumstance</th><th>Harm</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {{#each harmData.typical as |row|}}
            <tr><td>{{row.circumstance}}</td><td class="harm-val">{{row.harm}}</td></tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">Weapon Harm</div>
        <table class="kult-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Weapon</th><th>Harm</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {{#each harmData.weapons as |row|}}
            <tr><td>{{row.weapon}}</td><td class="harm-val">{{row.harm}}</td></tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">Serious Wounds</div>
        <p>Requires appropriate care and time to heal but won't worsen alone. Alcohol and painkillers can temporarily remove penalties. Max 4 — additional ones become Critical Wounds.</p>
        <p class="kult-muted"><em>Examples: lacerated arm, facial contusions, broken ribs, bone-deep cut, concussion, profuse bleeding, broken fingers, sprained ankle.</em></p>
      </div>

      <div class="kult-rule-card">
        <div class="kult-rule-title">Critical Wounds</div>
        <p>Will not heal on their own and will get worse if untreated. Requires urgent medical care to survive. Once stabilized and healed, treated as a stabilized Serious Wound.</p>
        <p class="kult-muted"><em>Examples: punctured lung, severed aorta, intestinal evisceration, ruptured eyeball, shattered collarbone, internal bleeding, spinal cord damage, cerebral hemorrhage.</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{! === UNIQUE MOVES TAB === }}
    <div class="tab-panel {{#if (eq currentTab 'unique')}}active{{/if}}" id="panel-unique">
      <div class="kult-filter-row">
        <button class="um-filter-btn {{#if (eq uniqueFilter 'all')}}active{{/if}}" data-cat="all">All</button>
        {{#each uniqueCategories as |cat|}}
        <button class="um-filter-btn {{#if (eq ../uniqueFilter cat)}}active{{/if}}" data-cat="{{cat}}">{{capitalize cat}}</button>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{#each uniqueMoves as |tiers cat|}}
      {{#unless (or (eq ../uniqueFilter 'all') (eq ../uniqueFilter cat))}}{{else}}
      <div class="kult-section-title">{{capitalize cat}} Moves</div>
      {{#each tiers as |moves tier|}}
      <div class="kult-um-tier">
        <div class="kult-tier-label"><span class="tier-badge">{{tier}}</span></div>
        <div class="moves-grid">
          {{#each moves as |move|}}
          <div class="move-chip" data-move="{{move}}" data-type="{{../cat}}">
            <span class="dot dot-tier-{{../../uniqueFilter}}"></span>
            <span>{{move}}</span>
          </div>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
      {{/unless}}
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    {{! === NPC BUILDER TAB === }}
    <div class="tab-panel {{#if (eq currentTab 'npc')}}active{{/if}}" id="panel-npc">
      <p class="kult-muted kult-hint">Click tags to build your NPC. Mix and match freely.</p>
      <div class="kult-npc-grid">
        {{#each npcData as |items category|}}
        <div class="kult-npc-category">
          <div class="kult-section-title">{{capitalize category}}</div>
          <div class="tag-cloud">
            {{#each items as |item|}}
            <span class="tag-item" data-category="{{../category}}" data-value="{{item}}">{{item}}</span>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
        </div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      <div class="kult-npc-actions">
        <button id="npc-generate" class="kult-btn">✦ Generate Random NPC</button>
        <button id="npc-clear" class="kult-btn kult-btn-muted">Clear</button>
      </div>
      <div id="npc-result"></div>
    </div>

    {{! === HORROR CONTRACT TAB === }}
    <div class="tab-panel {{#if (eq currentTab 'horror')}}active{{/if}}" id="panel-horror">
      <p class="kult-muted kult-hint">The GM's principles for creating horror at the table.</p>
      {{#each horrorContract as |item|}}
      <div class="kult-horror-item">
        <strong>{{item.title}}</strong>
        <span>{{item.desc}}</span>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    {{! === EXPERIENCE TAB === }}
    <div class="tab-panel {{#if (eq currentTab 'xp')}}active{{/if}}" id="panel-xp">
      <p class="kult-muted kult-hint">Check off questions answered this session.</p>
      {{#each experienceQuestions as |question i|}}
      <div class="kult-xp-item" data-index="{{i}}">
        <div class="kult-xp-check {{#if (lookup ../xpChecked i)}}checked{{/if}}" id="xp-check-{{i}}"></div>
        <span>{{question}}</span>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
      <div class="kult-xp-footer">
        <span class="kult-xp-label">SESSION TOTAL: <span id="xp-count">{{countTrue xpChecked}}</span> / 3 experience</span>
        <button id="xp-reset" class="kult-btn kult-btn-muted">Reset</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{! === GM CHAT TAB === }}
    <div class="tab-panel {{#if (eq currentTab 'chat')}}active{{/if}}" id="panel-chat">
      <p class="kult-muted kult-hint">Type commands or use shortcuts. Also works in Foundry chat as <code>/kult [command]</code>.</p>
      <div class="kult-quick-cmds">
        <button class="quick-cmd" data-cmd="/roll 2d10">/roll 2d10</button>
        <button class="quick-cmd" data-cmd="/move">/move</button>
        <button class="quick-cmd" data-cmd="/harm 2">/harm 2</button>
        <button class="quick-cmd" data-cmd="/stability">/stability</button>
        <button class="quick-cmd" data-cmd="/npc">/npc</button>
        <button class="quick-cmd" data-cmd="/wound serious">/wound serious</button>
        <button class="quick-cmd" data-cmd="/wound critical">/wound critical</button>
        <button class="quick-cmd" data-cmd="/help">/help</button>
      </div>
      <div id="chat-output" class="kult-chat-output"></div>
      <div class="kult-chat-input-row">
        <input id="chat-input" type="text" placeholder="Type a command or question..." />
        <button id="chat-send" class="kult-btn kult-btn-send">Send</button>
        <button id="chat-clear" class="kult-btn kult-btn-muted">Clear</button>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>{{! end .kult-body }}
</div>{{! end .kult-app-inner }}
